{
  "stem": "13851.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So the madness made them-- the Germans coming, the civilians who looking all those camps, what the Germans did, and buried those-- those people that were laying not buried-- the dead ones which didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in camp a few months there till we got by ourself strength back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, I told you, we went-- went back to Poland to see if anybody is alive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, Poland.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we ran away from Poland, because we could-- because I had saw in Poland they are anti-Semites and started killing people that came home to look for--",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, by train-- by-- by a train, because it's less.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We sat on the train with loading the coals on the locomotives.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We sat right on top of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we came like, all black.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For two nights.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we knew that's going to Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they signed with-- when they see maybe, look.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somebody is alive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It took a few nights-- a few days and nights, because, you know, they're going slow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you arrived in your town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The town was the same thing as we left, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then we talked to the-- one of the gentile people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, you survived?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we saw what-- we heard what's going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's-- there's a lot of-- there were something called AK, Armia Kryova.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Those were really those against the-- trying to kill the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So-- and we--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the war had ended--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--but there were still groups killing the Jews--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--when they went back home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that what's happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had pogroms in Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
